<http://model.geneontology.org/ev_w_id_R-HSA-5682888_R-HSA-5681999_controller_BFO_0000051_UniProtKB_Q9H0Y0_R-HSA-5682888_R-HSA-5681999_component_Reactome_R-HSA-1632852>
